Name: RHYUP
About the game: RHYUP is a challenging, 5 button rhythm game with shmup elements. Defend your home planet as you take control of a spaceship and move and shoot to the beat of the music while weaving through an onslaught of eye catching, enemy fire and boss fights all set to an amazing sound track of 20 unique songs and levels, each with 2 difficulty settings. Minimum requirements are for low settings 30+ FPS.
